No. 800, No. 969,

October Term, 1967.

October Term, 1967.

World Airways, Inc., et al. v. Pan American World Airways, Inc., et al.; and American Society of Travel Agents, Inc. v. Pan American World Airways, Inc., et al.,

391 IJ. S. 461. Motion for leave to supplement petition for rehearing granted. Petition for rehearing denied.

Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and petition.
